{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"CSS 数字工厂函数","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSS/factory_functions","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div class=\"notecard experimental\" id=\"sect1\"><p><strong>Experimental:</strong> <strong>这是一个实验中的功能</strong><br>此功能某些浏览器尚在开发中，请参考<a href=\"#browser_compatibility\">浏览器兼容性表格</a>以得到在不同浏览器中适合使用的前缀。由于该功能对应的标准文档可能被重新修订，所以在未来版本的浏览器中该功能的语法和行为可能随之改变。</p></div><strong>CSS numeric factory functions</strong>，例如 <code>CSS.em()</code> 和 <code>CSS.turn()</code>，是一组使用传入的数字参数以及所指定的单位（单位名称即所用方法名称）来返回 <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSUnitValue\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">CSSUnitValues (en-US)</a> 的方法。这些函数创建新的数字值，与使用 <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSUnitValue/CSSUnitValue\"><code>CSSUnitValue.CSSUnitValue()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> 构造函数相比，没有后者那么冗长。<p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"语法","title":"语法","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: plain notranslate\">CSS.number(number);\nCSS.percent(number);\n\n// &lt;length&gt;\nCSS.em(number);\nCSS.ex(number);\nCSS.ch(number);\nCSS.ic(number);\nCSS.rem(number);\nCSS.lh(number);\nCSS.rlh(number);\nCSS.vw(number);\nCSS.vh(number);\nCSS.vi(number);\nCSS.vb(number);\nCSS.vmin(number);\nCSS.vmax(number);\nCSS.cm(number);\nCSS.mm(number);\nCSS.Q(number);\nCSS.in(number);\nCSS.pt(number);\nCSS.pc(number);\nCSS.px(number);\n\n// &lt;angle&gt;\nCSS.deg(number);\nCSS.grad(number);\nCSS.rad(number);\nCSS.turn(number);\n\n// &lt;time&gt;\nCSS.s(number);\nCSS.ms(number);\n\n// &lt;frequency&gt;\nCSS.Hz(number);\nCSS.kHz(number);\n\n// &lt;resolution&gt;\nCSS.dpi(number);\nCSS.dpcm(number);\nCSS.dppx(number);\n\n// &lt;flex&gt;\nCSS.fr(number);\n</pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"示例","title":"示例","isH3":false,"content":"<p>我们使用 <code>CSS.vmax()</code> 数字工厂函数来创建一个 <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSUnitValue\"><code>CSSUnitValue</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>：</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> height <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token constant\">CSS</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">vmax</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">50</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span> height <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>       <span class=\"token comment\">// CSSUnitValue {value: 50, unit: \"vmax\"}</span>\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span> height<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>value <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>  <span class=\"token comment\">// 50</span>\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span> height<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>unit <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>   <span class=\"token comment\">// vmax</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>在这个例子中，我们给元素设定 margin 属性值，使用 <code>CSS.px()</code> 函数：</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>myElement<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>attributeStyleMap<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">set</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'margin'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token constant\">CSS</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">px</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">40</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> currentMargin <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> myElement<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>attributeStyleMap<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">get</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'margin'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>currentMargin<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>value<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> currentMargin<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>unit<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// 40, 'px'</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"规范","id":"规范","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://drafts.csswg.org/cssom/#namespacedef-css","title":"CSS Object Model (CSSOM)"}],"query":"api.CSS"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"query":"api.CSS","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSS/factory_functions/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"另请参阅","title":"另请参阅","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSUnitValue/CSSUnitValue\"><code>CSSUnitValue.CSSUnitValue()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"语法","id":"语法"},{"text":"示例","id":"示例"},{"text":"规范","id":"规范"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性"},{"text":"另请参阅","id":"另请参阅"}],"summary":"我们使用 CSS.vmax() 数字工厂函数来创建一个 CSSUnitValue (en-US)：","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"CSS numeric factory functions","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"CSS 数値ファクトリー関数","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/api/css/factory_functions","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/api/css/factory_functions/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API 接口参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSS","title":"CSS"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSS/factory_functions","title":"CSS 数字工厂函数"}],"pageTitle":"CSS 数字工厂函数 - Web API 接口参考 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}